     C* C1: READP walks SRFILE (keys 02,02,03) backward from past-EOF.
     C* Expect 3 successful reads then BOF. Exit 3.
     FSRTX    IP  F      80            DISK
     FSRFILE  IF  F      80  2AI     1 DISK
     ISRTX       01
     I                                        1   20STKEY
     ISRFILE     02
     I                                        1   20SKEY
     C           '99'      SETLLSRFILE                     
     C           RPL       TAG                             
     C                     READPSRFILE                   99
     C  99                 GOTO DONE                       
     C                     ADD  1         CNT              
     C                     GOTO RPL                        
     C           DONE      TAG                             
     CLR                   Z-ADDCNT       RPGRET           
